      "seq_in_scene": 1,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "四云童、四护从、四天将、天官同上。",
      "text_length": 17
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02001001_e00002",
      "play_id": "02001001",
      "scene_id": "02001001_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 2,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "醉花阴",
      "speakers": [
        "天官"
      ],
      "text": "雨顺风调，万民好，庆丰年，人人欢乐，似这等民安泰，乐滔滔。在华胥时，见了些人寿年丰，也不似清时妙，似这等官不差，民不扰，只俺奉玉旨将福禄褒。",
      "text_length": 70
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02001001_e00003",
      "play_id": "02001001",
      "scene_id": "02001001_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 3,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "天官归座。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02001001_e00004",
      "play_id": "02001001",
      "scene_id": "02001001_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 4,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "天官"
      ],
      "text": "瑞霭祥光紫雾腾，人间福主庆长生。欣看四海升平日，共沐恩波享太平。",
      "text_length": 32
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02001001_e00005",
      "play_id": "02001001",
      "scene_id": "02001001_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 5,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "天官"
      ],
      "text": "吾乃苍帝之子，上元一品，赐福天官是也。人间称为福德星君。所临之地，无不吉祥如意。今奉玉帝敕旨，因下界福主，乐善好施，阴功浩大，特邀诸位福神，前往下界，颁赐福禄，以彰积德之报。护从们，",
      "text_length": 91
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02001001_e00006",
      "play_id": "02001001",
      "scene_id": "02001001_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 6,
      "seq_in_scene": 6,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "众神"
      ],
      "text": "有。",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02001001_e00007",
      "play_id": "02001001",
      "scene_id": "02001001_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 7,
      "seq_in_scene": 7,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "天官"
      ],
      "text": "有请诸位星君。",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02001001_e00008",
      "play_id": "02001001",
      "scene_id": "02001001_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 8,
      "seq_in_scene": 8,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "众神"
      ],
      "text": "领法旨。有请诸位星君。",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02001001_e00009",
      "play_id": "02001001",
      "scene_id": "02001001_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 9,
      "seq_in_scene": 9,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "南极老人、牛郎、织女、张仙、财神同上。",
      "text_length": 19
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02001001_e00010",
      "play_id": "02001001",
      "scene_id": "02001001_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 10,
