      "speakers": [
        "天官"
      ],
      "text": "诸位福神少礼。",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02001001_e00025",
      "play_id": "02001001",
      "scene_id": "02001001_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 25,
      "seq_in_scene": 25,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "南极老人",
        "牛郎",
        "织女",
        "张仙",
        "财神"
      ],
      "text": "啊。上圣相召，有何台谕？",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02001001_e00026",
      "play_id": "02001001",
      "scene_id": "02001001_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 26,
      "seq_in_scene": 26,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "天官"
      ],
      "text": "吾奉玉帝敕旨，因下界福主，乐善好施，阴功浩大，故邀诸位福神，一同前往，颁赐福禄，以彰积德之报。",
      "text_length": 47
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02001001_e00027",
      "play_id": "02001001",
      "scene_id": "02001001_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 27,
      "seq_in_scene": 27,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "南极老人",
        "牛郎",
        "织女",
        "张仙",
        "财神"
      ],
      "text": "蒙颁上谕，敢不谨遵。",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02001001_e00028",
      "play_id": "02001001",
      "scene_id": "02001001_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 28,
      "seq_in_scene": 28,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "天官"
      ],
      "text": "护从们，",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02001001_e00029",
      "play_id": "02001001",
      "scene_id": "02001001_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 29,
      "seq_in_scene": 29,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "众神"
      ],
      "text": "有。",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02001001_e00030",
      "play_id": "02001001",
      "scene_id": "02001001_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 30,
      "seq_in_scene": 30,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "天官"
      ],
      "text": "驾起祥云，往福地去者。",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02001001_e00031",
      "play_id": "02001001",
      "scene_id": "02001001_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 31,
      "seq_in_scene": 31,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "众神"
      ],
      "text": "领法旨。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02001001_e00032",
      "play_id": "02001001",
      "scene_id": "02001001_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 32,
      "seq_in_scene": 32,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "众神同走圆场。",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02001001_e00033",
      "play_id": "02001001",
      "scene_id": "02001001_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 33,
      "seq_in_scene": 33,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "同喜迁莺",
      "speakers": [
        "众神"
      ],
      "text": "只羡他功深德浩，只羡他功深德浩，因此上赐福天曹逍也么遥。一门贤孝，恁看那福自天来，将官品超。争如为善好，这的是福禄自造，恁看他寿算弥高，恁看他寿算弥高。",
      "text_length": 76
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02001001_e00034",
      "play_id": "02001001",
      "scene_id": "02001001_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 34,
      "seq_in_scene": 34,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "众神"
      ],
      "text": "已到福地。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02001001_e00035",
      "play_id": "02001001",
      "scene_id": "02001001_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 35,
      "seq_in_scene": 35,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "南极老人",
        "牛郎",
        "织女",
        "张仙",
        "财神"
      ],
      "text": "请天官登台。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02001001_e00036",
      "play_id": "02001001",
      "scene_id": "02001001_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 36,
      "seq_in_scene": 36,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "〖吹打〗。天官上高台。",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02001001_e00037",
      "play_id": "02001001",
      "scene_id": "02001001_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 37,
      "seq_in_scene": 37,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "天官"
      ],
      "text": "妙哇！",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02001001_e00038",
      "play_id": "02001001",
      "scene_id": "02001001_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 38,
      "seq_in_scene": 38,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "天官"
      ],
      "text": "簇簇花香迎画阁，青青瑞草满阶庭。",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02001001_e00039",
      "play_id": "02001001",
      "scene_id": "02001001_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 39,
      "seq_in_scene": 39,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "天官"
      ],
      "text": "果然好福地也！",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02001001_e00040",
      "play_id": "02001001",
      "scene_id": "02001001_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 40,
      "seq_in_scene": 40,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "南极老人",
        "牛郎",
        "织女",
        "张仙",
        "财神"
      ],
      "text": "请天官赐福。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02001001_e00041",
      "play_id": "02001001",
      "scene_id": "02001001_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 41,
      "seq_in_scene": 41,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "天官"
      ],
      "text": "小圣奉玉帝敕旨，进爵一品，愿位列朝班，公侯世代。",
      "text_length": 24
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02001001_e00042",
      "play_id": "02001001",
      "scene_id": "02001001_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 42,
      "seq_in_scene": 42,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "南极老人",
        "牛郎",
        "织女",
        "张仙",
        "财神"
      ],
      "text": "天官赐福，正当如此。",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02001001_e00043",
      "play_id": "02001001",
      "scene_id": "02001001_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 43,
      "seq_in_scene": 43,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "天官"
      ],
      "text": "诸位福神，各将福禄赐之。",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02001001_e00044",
      "play_id": "02001001",
      "scene_id": "02001001_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 44,
      "seq_in_scene": 44,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "南极老人"
      ],
      "text": "老人无以为赠，进献百寿图一轴，愿福寿绵长，筹添海屋。",
      "text_length": 26
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02001001_e00045",
      "play_id": "02001001",
      "scene_id": "02001001_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 45,
      "seq_in_scene": 45,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "牛郎"
      ],
      "text": "小仙敬献年年如意，岁岁平安，愿稻生双穗，五谷丰登。",
      "text_length": 25
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02001001_e00046",
      "play_id": "02001001",
      "scene_id": "02001001_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 46,
      "seq_in_scene": 46,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "织女"
      ],
      "text": "织女敬献天丝文锦一缎，愿蚕桑茂盛，丝帛丰盈。",
      "text_length": 22
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02001001_e00047",
      "play_id": "02001001",
      "scene_id": "02001001_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 47,
      "seq_in_scene": 47,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "张仙"
      ],
      "text": "小仙特送麒麟为嗣，愿子孙繁衍，瓜瓞绵绵。",
      "text_length": 20
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02001001_e00048",
      "play_id": "02001001",
      "scene_id": "02001001_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 48,
      "seq_in_scene": 48,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "财神"
      ],
      "text": "俺财神特献黄金万两，愿财源茂盛，积玉堆金。",
      "text_length": 21
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02001001_e00049",
      "play_id": "02001001",
      "scene_id": "02001001_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 49,
      "seq_in_scene": 49,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "天官"
      ],
      "text": "妙哇！",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02001001_e00050",
      "play_id": "02001001",
      "scene_id": "02001001_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 50,
      "seq_in_scene": 50,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "同刮地风",
      "speakers": [
        "众神"
      ],
      "text": "哎呀，万千春，享富贵，乐滔滔，庆长春，酒泛香醪。看牛郎早报了田丰兆，织女献丝帛绫绡。积德的一门寿算，筹添海屋，南极星耀，福寿弥高，盈仓廪，稷米豆丰满仓廒。麒麟儿早登廊庙，佐皇家永享官爵。财源发，德行昭，乐善事，福禄根苗。你看那窦燕山五子登科早，又只见半空中魁星献的祥云来罩。",
      "text_length": 137
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02001001_e00051",
      "play_id": "02001001",
      "scene_id": "02001001_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 51,
      "seq_in_scene": 51,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "魁星上，跳舞，下。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02001001_e00052",
      "play_id": "02001001",
      "scene_id": "02001001_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 52,
      "seq_in_scene": 52,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "天官"
      ],
      "text": "魁星献瑞，万代全福也。",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02001001_e00053",
      "play_id": "02001001",
      "scene_id": "02001001_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 53,
      "seq_in_scene": 53,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "同水仙子",
      "speakers": [
        "众神"
      ],
      "text": "呀呀呀呀福分高，呀呀呀福分高。早早早，早佩着玉带金章把鼎鼐调，羡羡羡，羡文才锦绣好。看看看，看德门呈祥耀，贺贺贺，贺百福骈臻妙。庆庆庆，庆福门千祥照，道道道，道民乐欢天乐。拜拜拜，拜福主恩荣耀，俺俺俺，俺将这喜事儿留与后人标。",
      "text_length": 113
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02001001_e00054",
      "play_id": "02001001",
      "scene_id": "02001001_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 54,
      "seq_in_scene": 54,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "〖吹打〗。天官下高台，坐。",
      "text_length": 13
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02001001_e00055",
      "play_id": "02001001",
      "scene_id": "02001001_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 55,
      "seq_in_scene": 55,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "南极老人",
        "牛郎",
        "织女",
        "张仙",
        "财神"
      ],
      "text": "赐福已全。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02001001_e00056",
      "play_id": "02001001",
      "scene_id": "02001001_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 56,
      "seq_in_scene": 56,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "天官"
      ],
      "text": "一同覆奏上帝去者。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02001001_e00057",
      "play_id": "02001001",
      "scene_id": "02001001_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 57,
      "seq_in_scene": 57,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "南极老人",
        "牛郎",
        "织女",
        "张仙",
        "财神"
      ],
      "text": "请。",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02001001_e00058",
      "play_id": "02001001",
      "scene_id": "02001001_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 58,
      "seq_in_scene": 58,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "同煞尾",
      "speakers": [
        "众神"
      ],
      "text": "列旌幢一派仙音绕，一霎时神州赤县皆游到，只愿普天下积德的享福禄直到老。",
      "text_length": 35
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02001001_e00059",
      "play_id": "02001001",
      "scene_id": "02001001_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 59,
      "seq_in_scene": 59,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "〖吹打〗。众神同下。",
      "text_length": 10
    }
  ],
  "roles_inferred": true
}